<p>
Click to launch English version:
<ul>
<li><a href="glaciers.jnlp">Glaciers</a>
</ul>
<p>
<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>make boreholes start to fill in after 40 years, fully filled in after 60 years
<li>flags that are on the valley floor are deleted by an advancing glacier
<li>borehole drill remains on glacier's surface as the glacier evolves
<li>make GPS a permanent tool (it was "developer only"), add a nice image and value display
<li>remove labels on tools in toolbox, replace with "tool tips" that appear after a short delay
<li>add horizontal space between trash can and other tools in toolbox to differentiate it slightly
<li>fix ice thickness tool so that it doesn't fall apart when you drag it
<li>use the same font, border and layout in all tools that display values
</ul>
<p>
<b>Known problems:</b>
<ul>
<li>tools can be lost by dragging them outside the birds-eye view
</ul>
<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<ul>
<li>no debris/rocks moving in the ice
<li>ice doesn't appear to move
<li>snowfall is not visible
<li>time-based graphs are not implemented
<li>Advanced panel is hidden; what you see is the Basic panel
<li>no Help menu option to show pictures of real glaciers
</ul>
<p>
<b>Remaining work:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>see the <a href="http://phet.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/phet/trunk/simulations-java/simulations/glaciers/CHANGES.txt?view=markup">"to do" list</a>
</ul>
